```plantuml
@startuml SpeccyTV

component "User Interface" as UI {
    [Web Frontend]
    [Mobile App]
}

component "API Gateway" as Gateway {
    [movies_async_api]
    [movies_auth]
}

component "Streaming Services" as Streaming {
    [movies_streaming_converter]
    [movies_streaming_etl]
    [movies_streaming_admin]
}

component "Content Management" as Content {
    [movies_admin]
    [movies_async_api]
}

component "User Generated Content" as UGC {
    [movies_ugc]
    [Kafka]
    [ClickHouse]
}

component "Billing" as Billing {
    [movies_billing]
    [Stripe]
}

component "Data Stores" as Data {
    [PostgreSQL]
    [Elasticsearch]
    [Redis]
    [MinIO]
}

UI --> Gateway : HTTP/HTTPS
Gateway --> Streaming : gRPC/HTTP
Gateway --> Content : gRPC/HTTP
Gateway --> UGC : gRPC/HTTP
Gateway --> Billing : gRPC/HTTP

Streaming --> Data : Reads/Writes
Content --> Data : Reads/Writes
UGC --> Data : Reads/Writes
Billing --> Data : Reads/Writes

Streaming --> [FFmpeg] : Video Processing
movies_streaming_etl --> [Airflow] : Orchestration
movies_ugc --> Kafka : Event Streaming
movies_billing --> Stripe : Payment Processing

@enduml
```